Follow East Rockaway on Social Media

The district is keeping the community informed through social media.

From Rhame Avenue and Centre Avenue elementary schools to the Junior-Senior High School, administrators will show the activities taking place during school and after school. Please follow the social media accounts listed below to stay updated and to witness students and staff participate in several exciting and informal events.

